<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      }
      h2 {
        color: #2c3e50;
      }
      .otp {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #e74c3c;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Hello {{firstName}},</h2>
      <p>Thank you for signing up with <strong>FX Trading App</strong>.</p>
      <p>Please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to verify your account:</p>
      <div class="otp">{{otp}}</div>
      <p>This OTP will expire in <strong>5 minutes</strong>. Do not share it with anyone.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br/>Wilson's Team</p>
      <div class="footer">
        If you did not request this, please ignore this email.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
